data.description: Well maintained beauty! This home starts with beautiful curb appeal.  Open floor plan upgraded carpet and two-tone paint t/o. Large windows allow great natural light.  Popular white kitchen with stainless steel appliance. A breakfast bar, dine in kitchen and formal dining area in living room offer an array of entertainment options. A fireplace ensures warmth on those cool evenings. The primary bedroom is spacious w/ a beautifully executed double vanities and exquisite garden tub. A walk-in shower and closet create your ideal ensuite. AZ outdoor living abounds out under your covered patio with mountain views! Home equipped with Solar.  Loan is transferrable. Make this your home today!!
